pulses.name: 20250122 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
22 Jan 2025 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- China (CN) - China is a significant source of cyber activities, with multiple instances of the Mozi botnet and various attacks exploiting vulnerabilities in devices such as D-Link and Dasan GPON routers.
United States (US) - The US shows a high frequency of attacks, including the SystemBC botnet and Back Orifice traffic, indicating substantial malicious activity originating from this region.
India (IN) - India is notable for numerous attacks involving remote command injection vulnerabilities in multiple routers, reflecting a concentrated effort to exploit known weaknesses in network devices.
